name: A BOWL OF CONFUSING WORLD
description:
Have you ever realized that almost every day we consume something from the world that is unacceptable to the mind and not infrequently it makes us wonder why this is so?

This is my tribute to one of my favorite artist:
ALWAYSYUDHIS

3000x4000 px
500 dpi
77 unique doodle characters
+ some of florals
